about.description:
This package offers a set of common detectors, transformers and aggregators
with unified APIs, as well as pipe classes that connect them together into
models. It also provides some functions to process and visualize
time series and anomaly events.
about.summary: A package for unsupervised time series anomaly detection

name: adtk
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "adtk" %}
{% set version = "0.6.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6cfafb44b5ad26a2ffd640aeb79d84fc5383d2d42c97a47420695badbee27be8

build:
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - python >=3.5
    - pandas >=0.23
    - numpy >=1.15
    - matplotlib-base >=3.0
    - scikit-learn >=0.20
    - statsmodels <0.11,>=0.9
    - packaging >=17.0
    - tabulate >=0.8

test:
  imports:
    - adtk

about:
  home: https://github.com/arundo/adtk
  license: MPL-2.0
  license_family: MOZILLA
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A package for unsupervised time series anomaly detection
  description: |
    This package offers a set of common detectors, transformers and aggregators
    with unified APIs, as well as pipe classes that connect them together into 
    models. It also provides some functions to process and visualize 
    time series and anomaly events.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - rpanai
smithy_version:
No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
3.6.16
